I couldn't even sleep.

8
00:00:30,908 --> 00:00:35,521
Right? I never imagined
my own kid would be the bully.

9
00:00:35,561 --> 00:00:37,870
If it were me,
I'd smack the crap out of 'em.

10
00:00:38,686 --> 00:00:41,416
You totally seem like
you were a bully, Midori.

11
00:00:41,617 --> 00:00:44,529
I was bullied by types
like you, Midori.

12
00:00:44,857 --> 00:00:48,330
Not me! I was a total
justice-warrior delinquent.

13
00:00:49,750 --> 00:00:52,149
It's ready, everyone! Let's eat!

14
00:00:52,283 --> 00:00:53,484
Hold on!

15
00:00:53,496 --> 00:00:54,709
You're hungry, right?

16
00:00:55,190 --> 00:00:57,727
Anyway, listen to my
