right now.

25
00:01:08,136 --> 00:01:10,350
- Okay, okay, okay.
- We're eating, we're eating!

26
00:01:10,414 --> 00:01:11,620
Eat your food.

27
00:01:11,885 --> 00:01:13,091
Hear our story, too.

28
00:01:13,577 --> 00:01:14,817
- Right.
- No, no.

29
00:01:14,856 --> 00:01:16,064
I'll hear you out.

30
00:01:19,814 --> 00:01:22,014
Alright!

31
00:01:25,065 --> 00:01:26,696
