32
00:01:27,143 --> 00:01:28,750
Yay!

33
00:01:29,108 --> 00:01:30,583
Thank you!

34
00:01:33,534 --> 00:01:34,950
Here we go.

35
00:01:41,997 --> 00:01:44,800
