62
00:03:41,348 --> 00:03:44,290
Women do it naturally, so when guys
brag about it, it's infuriating.

63
00:03:44,330 --> 00:03:50,962
I mean, it's not like I'm bragging,
but with sex, I just don't know what to do.

64
00:03:51,002 --> 00:03:54,530
But you're still trying, right?
I think that's admirable.

65
00:03:54,556 --> 00:03:58,318
Seriously admirable. If my husband wanted it,
I'd let him every night.

66
00:03:58,637 --> 00:04:04,737
She keeps turning me down. Makes me wonder
