67
00:04:05,070 --> 00:04:06,430
Just crawl into her futon!

68
00:04:07,330 --> 00:04:10,690
No no no, impossible.
She'd knock me out.

69
00:04:12,047 --> 00:04:15,161
Plus Taro sleeps with her,
