72
00:04:18,385 --> 00:04:19,659
How about texting?

73
00:04:19,716 --> 00:04:22,976
Apparently my husband's friend
asks his wife over texting.

74
00:04:23,230 --> 00:04:25,970
Gross! Gross! What is that?
Absolutely not.

75
00:04:26,010 --> 00:04:30,290
That's great! Getting a text like that
