76
00:04:30,669 --> 00:04:31,950
Send it! Send it!

77
00:04:31,990 --> 00:04:33,218
Want me to write it for you?

78
00:04:33,258 --> 00:04:34,829
- No, I'm good.
- Send it! Send it!

79
00:04:34,869 --> 00:04:35,970
Now! Now! Send it now!

80
00:04:36,010 --> 00:04:37,409
Now! Now! Now!

81
00:04:37,525 --> 00:04:39,263
Send it! Send it!

82
