90
00:05:09,578 --> 00:05:13,811
That'll be 2,239 yen. Sir?

91
00:05:14,156 --> 00:05:18,690
2,239 yen, please. Sir?

92
00:05:19,101 --> 00:05:22,616
How do they even come up with stuff
like the Dick Dance? Makes no sense.

93
00:05:22,822 --> 00:05:27,636
