what to write.

94
00:05:28,479 --> 00:05:33,667
"Might I humbly request intercourse?
Thank you for your consideration."

95
00:05:34,276 --> 00:05:38,636
Should I be that submissive?
Or maybe keep it light...

96
00:05:39,275 --> 00:05:42,170
"I wanna have sex.
How about it?"

97
00:05:42,841 --> 00:05:44,709
What should I even send?

98
00:05:44,749 --> 00:05:47,516
