She wrote most of it last time, right?
You even brought her to the meeting.

137
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:16,436
No, she just helped a little.
I had a lot of work overlapping.

138
00:08:16,660 --> 00:08:22,000
What, already getting shy? The directors
