139
00:08:22,188 --> 00:08:27,948
Nishimura was going on about
how gorgeous she is, all worked up.

140
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:30,775
Said she's too good for you.

141
00:08:31,342 --> 00:08:34,296
Oh right, Nishimura's probably
directing this one too.

142
00:08:34,656 --> 00:08:39,403
What, you don't like that? But Nishimura
specifically asked for you to write it.

143
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:44,576
Wait... maybe he just wants
to see your wife again?

144
00:08:48,445 --> 00:08:52,096
Oh, that reminds me.
I got myself a sex friend.

145
00:08:52,141 --> 00:08:53,380
