My sex tape.

147
00:08:57,997 --> 00:09:02,836
Just so you know, it's not like that.
I didn't pull any producer privileges.

148
00:09:03,109 --> 00:09:08,226
There's sites for finding sex friends.
You should sign up, Yanagida.

149
00:09:08,544 --> 00:09:14,397
It's such a great arrangement, you know?
Totally win-win.

150
00:09:16,665 --> 00:09:23,056
While thinking what an idiot this guy was,
I found myself shamefully aroused.

151
00:09:23,409 --> 00:09:27,317
Okay, that's enough.
Want me to send you the video?

152
00:09:28,700 --> 00:09:30,060
No thanks.

153
00:09:30,337 --> 00:09:33,390
Right. Can't risk it
getting spread around.

154
00:09:33,900 --> 00:09:35,603
Anyway, I'll leave it to you.

155
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:40,076
Oh, Nishimura's coming with us
to the doctor's tomorrow.

156
00:09:40,566 --> 00:09:42,430
Um, you know, the same doctor as before.

157
00:09:42,504 --> 00:09:44,006
Oh, the internist?

158
00:09:44,046 --> 00:09:45,803
Yeah, yeah, that's right.

159
00:09:46,283 --> 00:09:47,485
Did you get a boner?

160
00:09:51,326 --> 00:09:56,016
Yoyogi's video had ignited
my sexual desire.

161
00:09:59,888 --> 00:10:05,356
Sorry for the sudden ask. Could we
possibly have sex tonight?

162
00:10:05,742 --> 00:10:09,290
I figured your period should be
over by now...

163
00:10:35,183 --> 00:10:37,750
Message read

164
00:10:46,590 --> 00:10:47,795
