167
00:10:52,490 --> 00:10:54,475
Oh, you ate all the PL fried rice!

168
00:10:54,515 --> 00:10:55,515
Yep.

169
00:10:55,546 --> 00:10:59,361
Taro, what do you want for dinner?
Wanna go shopping together?

170
00:10:59,710 --> 00:11:03,781
Nah, can I see the iPad instead?
I was reading manga all day.

171
00:11:03,810 --> 00:11:05,281
Oh, hang on a sec.

172
00:11:10,126 --> 00:11:13,346
Chika

173
00:11:13,934 --> 00:11:15,688
- Yes?
- What are you doing?

174
00:11:15,701 --> 00:11:17,610
I told you we have the school
counselor today.

175
00:11:17,650 --> 00:11:19,356
See, I knew you forgot.

176
00:11:20,596 --> 00:11:22,750
Sorry, I'm coming right now. Where are you?

177
00:11:28,371 --> 00:11:30,376
Here, your iPad.

178
00:11:30,684 --> 00:11:32,904
Taro, Daddy's going to your school, okay?

179
00:11:32,967 --> 00:11:33,980
Okay, I'm off.

180
00:11:34,020 --> 00:11:35,500
Bye-bye!

181
00:11:37,964 --> 00:11:41,336
