183
00:12:00,239 --> 00:12:03,236
I'm so sorry I'm late.

184
00:12:03,258 --> 00:12:05,458
What are you doing, late every time?

185
00:12:05,626 --> 00:12:08,163
Sorry, I was making dinner
and lost track of time.

186
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:10,360
You make dinner?

187
00:12:10,380 --> 00:12:12,460
Yeah, cooking's my department.

188
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:15,800
Enough showing off. This isn't about you,
it's about Taro.

189
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:16,840
Right, of course.

190
00:12:16,874 --> 00:12:19,210
I'm so sorry about him, Mr. Maemura.

191
00:12:19,820 --> 00:12:28,436
Well, he hasn't had many tantrums
