so let's keep monitoring things.

212
00:13:48,180 --> 00:13:50,256
He is making progress.

213
00:13:51,663 --> 00:13:53,420
Thank you so much, really.

214
00:13:53,727 --> 00:13:54,930
Thank you.

215
00:13:57,271 --> 00:14:02,920
Taro's really growing, isn't he?
I never imagined him talking about us.

216
00:14:03,043 --> 00:14:05,949
I do think he's growing little by little.

217
00:14:06,189 --> 00:14:12,302
Before, just going to school would set off
